         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" id="d3108e14">Economic Purchase Quantity-Supplies <ph outputclass="SmCaps">(Aug 1987)</ph>
         </p>
         <ol id="d3074e25">
            <li>
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3108e20">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
						            Offerors are invited to state an opinion on whether the quantity(ies) of supplies on which bids, proposals or quotes are requested in this solicitation is (are) economically advantageous to the Government.</p>
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3108e24">
                  <cite outputclass="MultiLine" xtrc="52.207-4_d1e39" xtrf="VFI">_________________________________________________________________________________ </cite>
